      "      \"officialTitle\": \"A Phase 3 Prospective, Blinded, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, International Multicenter Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of a Single SQ Injection of Zalunfiban in Subjects With ST-elevation MI in the Pre-hospital Setting\",\n",
