      "          \"name\": \"zalunfiban\",\n",
      "          \"description\": \"zalunfiban is a novel small molecule inhibitor of the platelet \\u03b1IIb\\u03b23 receptor specifically designed for first medical contact therapy of ST-elevation myocardial infarction (STEMI).\",\n",
      "          \"armGroupLabels\": [\n",
      "            \"zalunfiban Dose 1 (0.110 mg/kg)\",\n",
